title: Protesters outside Liberal Party meeting label pre-selection process for Joe Hockey's Sydney seat 'undemocratic'
text: A small group of people stage a protest outside the Liberal Party's pre-selection meeting for former treasurer Joe Hockey's seat of North Sydney, labelling the process "undemocratic". ...
